## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="a527a-102">Zdarzenia są wywoływane <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SpeechRecognizer> przez klasy i <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SpeechRecognitionEngine>. `SpeechDetected`</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a527a-102">A `SpeechDetected` event is raised by the <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SpeechRecognizer> and <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SpeechRecognitionEngine> classes.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="a527a-103">Zdarzenia **SpeechDetected** są generowane, gdy aparat rozpoznawania może identyfikować dane wejściowe audio jako ludzkie mowę.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a527a-103">**SpeechDetected** events are generated when a recognition engine can identify audio input as human speech.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="a527a-104"><xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SpeechDetectedEventArgs>pochodzi od <xref:System.EventArgs>.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a527a-104"><xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SpeechDetectedEventArgs> derives from <xref:System.EventArgs>.</span></span>  
  
   
  
## Examples  
 <span data-ttu-id="a527a-105">Poniższy przykład tworzy procedurę obsługi dla <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SpeechRecognizer.SpeechDetected?displayProperty=nameWithType> lub <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SpeechRecognitionEngine.SpeechDetected?displayProperty=nameWithType> zdarzeń.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a527a-105">The example below creates a handler for <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SpeechRecognizer.SpeechDetected?displayProperty=nameWithType> or <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SpeechRecognitionEngine.SpeechDetected?displayProperty=nameWithType> events.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a527a-106">Program obsługi inicjuje wyświetlanie za każdym razem, gdy wykryto mowę i wyświetla informacje o stanie, w tym pozycję audio.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a527a-106">The handler initializes a display every time speech is detected and displays status information, including audio position.</span></span>  
  
```  
_recognizer.SpeechDetected +=  
  delegate(object sender, SpeechDetectedEventArgs eventArgs)   
  {  
  
    // Clear previous recognition information.  
    _audioDeviceStatusLabel.Enabled = true;  
    _audioDeviceStatusLabel.Visible = true;  
    Utils.DisplayAudioInputFormat(_audioStateLabel, _recognizer);  
    Utils.DisplayRecognizerState(_recognizerStateLabel, _recognizer.State);  
    Utils.DisplaySpeechDetected(_speechDetectedLabel, eventArgs.AudioPosition);  
  };  
```

  
  
## Examples  
 <span data-ttu-id="a527a-109">Poniższy przykład tworzy procedurę obsługi dla <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SpeechRecognizer.SpeechDetected?displayProperty=nameWithType> lub <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SpeechRecognitionEngine.SpeechDetected?displayProperty=nameWithType> zdarzeń.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a527a-109">The example below creates a handler for <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SpeechRecognizer.SpeechDetected?displayProperty=nameWithType> or <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SpeechRecognitionEngine.SpeechDetected?displayProperty=nameWithType> events.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a527a-110">Procedura obsługi inicjuje wyświetlanie przy każdym wykryciu mowy i wyświetla informacje o stanie, w tym pozycję audio.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a527a-110">The handler initializes a display each time speech is detected and displays status information, including audio position.</span></span>  
  
```  
_recognizer.SpeechDetected +=  
  delegate(object sender, SpeechDetectedEventArgs eventArgs)   
  {  
  
    // Clear previous recognition information.  
    _audioDeviceStatusLabel.Enabled = true;  
    _audioDeviceStatusLabel.Visible = true;  
    Utils.DisplayAudioInputFormat(_audioStateLabel, _recognizer);  
    Utils.DisplayRecognizerState(_recognizerStateLabel, _recognizer.State);  
    Utils.DisplaySpeechDetected(_speechDetectedLabel, eventArgs.AudioPosition);  
  };  
```
